e control that was tapped.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you specify is a descendant of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"text":" class,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view via the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"text":" method, you can specify the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"custom accessory views using the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"leftAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rightAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"type":"heading","text":"Related examples"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L982","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:":{"type":"topic","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swi